article_id:74,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Storm Sentinel Clash [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>During the Storm Sentinel Clash event boss battle, Storm Sentinel using Orbital Drones can cause the game to hang.</div><div>We have found that this issue occurs across all difficulty levels.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue.</div><div>Any further updates regarding this issue will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1540989600"></span>]</strong></span><br>This issue can be resolved by closing and reopening the game.<br>We are currently investigating this issue. Any further update regarding this issue will be added to this notice.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1540979100,update_time1542364217